---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const siteUrl = 'https://weddingroomdecoration.com';
const phoneNumber = '+923227555459';
const whatsappUrl = `https://wa.me/923227555459`;
const pageTitle = 'Wedding Room Decoration Items Checklist Lahore';
const pageDescription = 'Quick list of wedding room decoration items in Lahore with simple guidance on what to include and book.';
const canonical = `${siteUrl}/wedding-room-decoration-items/`;
---

<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} canonical={canonical}>
  <section class="space-y-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-rose-700">Wedding Room Decoration Items</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Knowing which wedding room decoration items to use keeps the setup balanced and on-budget. We help Lahore families choose essentials like petals, fresh flowers, fairy lights, and tidy backdrops so the room looks special without feeling crowded. Share your room photos and budget, and we’ll tailor a shortlist that fits your timing. Each item is priced transparently before booking, and WhatsApp updates keep planning quick.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Starting Price / Range</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">Starter kits focus on petals and lights, with add-ons for florals, frames, candles, and props as needed.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">What’s Included</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-700 space-y-1">
      <li>Bed and headboard styling materials</li>
      <li>Lighting, candles, or LED candles for ambience</li>
      <li>Fresh flowers, petals, vases, and optional signage</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Designs / Products</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">We suggest combinations of petals, fairy lights, floral points, and frames suited to your room size and photos.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Best For</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">Couples who want a clear checklist of décor items before booking a full setup.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">How Booking Works</h2>
    <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 text-gray-700 space-y-1">
      <li>Share your room photos and budget on WhatsApp.</li>
      <li>Receive a shortlist of recommended items with price notes.</li>
      <li>Confirm selections; team brings everything and sets it up.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">FAQs</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-700 space-y-1">
      <li>Which items are reusable after the event?</li>
      <li>Can we request fragrance-free candles or flowers?</li>
      <li>Do you supply extension cords for lights?</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Book Now</h2>
    <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
      <p>Message us for a customized decoration items list with upfront pricing.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href={whatsappUrl} class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-rose-600 px-4 py-2 text-white font-semibold shadow hover:bg-rose-700 transition" aria-label={`Chat on WhatsApp at ${phoneNumber}`}>WhatsApp Us</a>
        <a href="/wedding-room-decoration-prices/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-rose-600 px-4 py-2 text-rose-700 font-semibold hover:bg-rose-50 transition">View Prices</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-gray-800 font-semibold hover:bg-gray-50 transition">Contact Form</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
